videos.description: Xavier Sneed intercepts a bad pass and takes it all the way to the rack for an emphatic slam for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Sneed climbs ladder for big slam

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk gets the dish from Malik Newman and knocks down the deep ball for the Jayhawks .
videos.headline: Kansas' Mykhailiuk drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Barry Brown Jr. takes a hard hit to the face from Devonte' Graham in the first half, causing him to exit the game.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Brown leaves with eye injury

videos.description: Mike McGuirl blows by his defender and drops in the flashy left layup for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kansas State's McGuirl sinks pretty and-1 layup

videos.description: Cartier Diarra lobs to Xavier Sneed who slams home a thunderous two-handed jam, igniting the Wildcat bench.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Sneed throws down monster alley-oop

videos.description: Mitch Lightfoot comes out of nowhere  to shut down Makol Mawien in the second half for the Jayhwaks.
videos.headline: Kansas' Lightfoot hustles for big block
